{"title":"Linux下安装部署ActiveMQ","date":"2018-09-12T11:08:23.000Z","slug":"Linux下安装部署ActiveMQ","tags":["MQ"],"categories":["Linux"],"updated":"2018-09-12T11:20:56.245Z","content":"<h2 id=\"一、下载解压文件\"><a href=\"#一、下载解压文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、下载解压文件\"></a>一、下载解压文件</h2><p>  下载页面 ：<a href=\"http://activemq.apache.org/activemq-5155-release.html。点击下载最新版本即可。\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://activemq.apache.org/activemq-5155-release.html。点击下载最新版本即可。</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"二、上传文件到linux服务器上\"><a href=\"#二、上传文件到linux服务器上\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、上传文件到linux服务器上\"></a>二、上传文件到linux服务器上</h2><p>可以使用rz命令，将下载的本地文件拖拽到虚拟机窗口就可以完成上传。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/easyhaloo/easyhaloo.github.io/master/image/activemq1.png\" alt=\"服务图\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"三、解压文件\"><a href=\"#三、解压文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、解压文件\"></a>三、解压文件</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd  解压的activemq文件目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">tar -zxvf 文件名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"四、启动\"><a href=\"#四、启动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、启动\"></a>四、启动</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">启动服务</span><br><span class=\"line\">bin/activemq start</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">查看启动状态</span><br><span class=\"line\">bin/activemq status</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">停止服务</span><br><span class=\"line\">bin/activemq stop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"五、设置开机启动，并注册为系统服务\"><a href=\"#五、设置开机启动，并注册为系统服务\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、设置开机启动，并注册为系统服务\"></a>五、设置开机启动，并注册为系统服务</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">建立软连接</span><br><span class=\"line\">ln -s /root/apache-activemq-5.15.5/bin/activemq /etc/init.d</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">设置开启启动</span><br><span class=\"line\">chkconfig activemq on</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">通过系统指令</span><br><span class=\"line\">service activemq start</span><br><span class=\"line\">service activemq status</span><br><span class=\"line\">service activemq stop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"六、开放端口的防火墙\"><a href=\"#六、开放端口的防火墙\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"六、开放端口的防火墙\"></a>六、开放端口的防火墙</h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">firewall-cmd --zone=public --add-port=8161/tcp --permanent</span><br><span class=\"line\">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"七、查看管控台\"><a href=\"#七、查看管控台\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"七、查看管控台\"></a>七、查看管控台</h2><p>直接在本地开启浏览器访问：Linux的地址加上8161端口。使用admin/admin登录。<br><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/easyhaloo/easyhaloo.github.io/master/image/activemq2.png\" alt=\"服务图\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"注意：\"><a href=\"#注意：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意：\"></a>注意：</h2><p>如果之前你已经安装其他的mq，有可能会造成端口冲突。查看activemq的日志，在activemq文件夹的data目录下，有一个activemq.log文件。打开查看详细。如下：<br><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/easyhaloo/easyhaloo.github.io/master/image/activemq3.png\" alt=\"服务图\"></p>\n<p>无法注册到amqp上，说明端口被占用。</p>\n<p> 此时需要修改activemq的配置文件：</p>\n<p> 修改activemq文件夹下的conf/activemq.xml。更改ampq的端口即可。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/easyhaloo/easyhaloo.github.io/master/image/activemq4.png\" alt=\"服务图\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"SpringBoot 2.0.5.RELEASE 中文翻译笔记Getting Starte","slug":"SpringBoot-2-0-5-RELEASE-中文翻译笔记Getting-Starte"},"next":{"title":"Zuul多路径访问时报404问题","slug":"Zuul多路径访问时报404问题"},"link":"https://easyhaloo.github.io/post/Linux下安装部署ActiveMQ/","toc":[{"title":"一、下载解压文件","id":"一、下载解压文件","index":"1"},{"title":"二、上传文件到linux服务器上","id":"二、上传文件到linux服务器上","index":"2"},{"title":"三、解压文件","id":"三、解压文件","index":"3"},{"title":"四、启动","id":"四、启动","index":"4"},{"title":"五、设置开机启动，并注册为系统服务","id":"五、设置开机启动，并注册为系统服务","index":"5"},{"title":"六、开放端口的防火墙","id":"六、开放端口的防火墙","index":"6"},{"title":"七、查看管控台","id":"七、查看管控台","index":"7"},{"title":"注意：","id":"注意：","index":"8"}],"copyright":true}